# Collecting and mapping Census data using API: State data and maps

library(tidycensus)
library(mapview)
options(tigris_use_cache = TRUE)


nj_income <- get_acs(
  geography = "tract", 
  variables = "B19013_001",
  state = "NJ", 
  year = 2020,
  geometry = TRUE
)

library(tmap)
tmap_mode("view")

essex_income <- get_acs(
  geography = "tract",
  variables = "B19013_001",
  year = 2020,
  state = "NJ",
  county = "Essex",
  geometry = TRUE
)

tm_shape(essex_income) + 
  tm_fill(col = "estimate", palette = "YlOrRd",
          alpha = 0.5)
mapView(essex_income, zcol = "estimate")
